<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Info is correct...this is a sweet weapon and is by all means taunterrfic.  It has the same animation as the old Painbringer from the Kolbold Champion in Sol.  Much better weapon by far though.  If it didnt have the stats on it it would cost as much, but it does -GOOD- so good luck buying one. =)</font></td></tr></table>
