<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Your stats suck bro.  Sorry to break the news.  Anywho the sword is damn nice.  Me and a few people in my guild camped this for 13 hours and only 1 lamentation dropped and the stupid mask dropped so often it made you wanna puke.  The bow never dropped.  We had me (54 Warrior) 53 Enchanter, 54 Cleric, 53 Monk, 58 Necro, and a 56 Wizzie.  We took everything in the area very easily and I got me a sword.  <BR>
<BR>
I duel wield this and another lam (which I had to buy **grumble grumble**) I dont hit taunt anymore its pretty nice completely took it off my hotkeys.  Make sure as a warrior though some info I can give is to work on other skills to.  Buy a Bloodpoint if you can and a Jade Mace.<BR>
